---
title: Indian Lentil, Chicken & Cauliflower Dhal Filo Pie with Roasted Veggies
description: A dhal in a pie is too good to be true, but here are the facts to prove that this is indeed the best pie in town. You can’t dispute a chicken and veggie-packed filling complete with lentils and cauliflower when there’s a bunch of flavours including hints of coconut. A crunchy filo pastry on top seals the deal. Case closed, the dhal filo pie wins!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

